&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, it’s a foreign concept in the development of healthcare tech.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;google-trends-embed&quot;&gt;
  &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;https://ssl.gstatic.com/trends_nrtr/760_RC04/embed_loader.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
